Roll the ball to the green goal button at the end of each level to progress!

[b]CONTROLS[/b]
• [b]Arrow Keys[/b] or [b]WASD[/b]: Move platforms to guide the ball
• [b]R[/b]: Reset the current level
• [b]P[/b]: Pause/Unpause the game 

[b]GAMEPLAY[/b]
• Use moving platforms to navigate the ball through obstacles
• Collect coins along the way for points
• Avoid falling off the platforms or hitting barriers
• Press buttons to toggle barriers and unlock paths
• Use springs to launch the ball to higher platforms

[b]PLATFORM TYPES[/b]
• [b]Static Platforms[/b]: Don't move - use them as stable ground
• [b]Uniaxial Platforms[/b]: Move left and right
• [b]Biaxial Platforms[/b]: Move in all four directions (left, right, forward, back)

Good luck and have fun!"

